{"tid":1974067,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"李慧琼稱政府有責任考慮就23條立法維護國家安全","createTime":"2020-04-15T15:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T15:15:23.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"14c2e6302b1652ede801de27f4ace258f862dced","tid":1974067,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:04:04.000Z","msg":"<strong>中聯辦主任駱惠寧認為，香港自回歸以來，在維護國家安全問題上，不夠完善。</strong><br />\n<br />\n民建聯主席、立法會議員李慧琼說，一國兩制有制度優勢，但不能夠成為國家安全的缺口。她認為，反修例運動期間，有議員到外國邀請外國政府干預香港事務，反映國家安全存有漏洞，特區政府有責任去維護國家安全，例如考慮就基本法23條立法以堵塞漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520794-20200415.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520794-20200415.htm&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgEWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=306c8a22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520794-20200415.htm&h=6f4ca9f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520794-20200415.htm</a>"},{"pid":"964b2fe9dc461d3b7020d41889cbced7137b80c6","tid":1974067,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:15:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">永屌23條</span>"}]}